{"tid":1948694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】130萬個中國製口罩品質不合標準 60萬個送醫院荷蘭急回收","createTime":"2020-03-29T07:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T08:30:02.000Z","uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"397752115ab69f35e3b3070a771eee403db5dbde","tid":1948694,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/yTWEvZNuomtJEcPTRfzN1dlKr6k=/414x232/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/JCSJ7XCT33EC7EB3ILMB3UIXWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FyTWEvZNuomtJEcPTRfzN1dlKr6k%3D%2F414x232%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FJCSJ7XCT33EC7EB3ILMB3UIXWQ.jpg&h=c148ecac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國周六宣佈向中國大量訂購口罩抗疫之際，荷蘭回收數十萬個從中國入口的口罩，原因是質量未達標準。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭衞生部周六表示，本月21日收到那批中國製口罩，第一次檢測時已發現有問題，但有一部份已送往醫院。當局立即停止發送餘下口罩，同時在第二次檢測中確定口罩是次貨，用不得。衞生部表示，以後會對訂購的口罩進行額外檢測。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭公共電視台NOS報道，涉事的130萬個中國製口FFP2級別口罩，有60萬個已分發到醫院。報道指，那批口罩未能緊貼用者臉部，濾材亦有問題。<br />\n<br />\n法新社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200329/PCTMJW534VI4R4TG66MH4VDBH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200329%2FPCTMJW534VI4R4TG66MH4VDBH4%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJew1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=9bcdc5ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200329%2FPCTMJW534VI4R4TG66MH4VDBH4%2F&h=b3438ec8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200329/PCTMJW534VI4R4TG66MH4VDBH4/</a>"},{"pid":"e0593328a591814aef8e3e9f69b392f04635c733","tid":1948694,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"甴共平領導之下嘅蝗國，慣咗生產啲劣質嘢，今次真係可以响國際舞台上大放異彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}